<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Eviction Defense AI</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Educational eviction guidance to help tenants understand notices, timelines, and next steps. Not legal advice." />
  <meta name="robots" content="index,follow" />

  <style>
    :root{
      --bg:#f6f7fb;
      --card:#ffffff;
      --text:#15171a;
      --muted:#5b6472;
      --border:rgba(20,24,30,.10);
      --shadow:0 18px 50px rgba(16,24,40,.10);
      --radius:16px;
      --accent:#111827;
      --accent2:#0f172a;
    }

    *{ box-sizing:border-box; }
    body{
      margin:0;
      font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      color:var(--text);
      background: radial-gradient(1200px 800px at 20% -10%, rgba(15,23,42,.12), transparent 60%),
                  radial-gradient(900px 600px at 90% 0%, rgba(17,24,39,.10), transparent 55%),
                  var(--bg);
      line-height:1.55;
    }

    a{ color:#0b5fff; text-decoration:none; }
    a:hover{ text-decoration:underline; }

    .wrap{ max-width:980px; margin:0 auto; padding:28px 18px 60px; }

    .topbar{
      display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between;
      gap:14px; margin-bottom:18px;
    }
    .brand{
      display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px; font-weight:800;
      letter-spacing:.2px;
    }
    .dot{
      width:12px; height:12px; border-radius:999px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #111827, #334155);
      box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.18);
    }

    .pill{
      font-size:12px; padding:8px 12px; border:1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius:999px; background:rgba(255,255,255,.7);
      color:var(--muted);
      backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    }

    .hero{
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,.95), rgba(255,255,255,.82));
      border:1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      padding: 30px 22px;
    }
    h1{ margin:0 0 10px; font-size: clamp(28px, 3.2vw, 42px); letter-spacing:-.5px; }
    .sub{ margin:0 0 18px; color:var(--muted); font-size: 16px; max-width: 72ch; }

    .grid{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap:14px;
      margin-top:18px;
    }
    @media(min-width:860px){
      .grid{ grid-template-columns: 1.1fr .9fr; }
    }

    .card{
      background: var(--card);
      border:1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 18px;
      box-shadow: 0 14px 40px rgba(16,24,40,.08);
    }
    .card h2{ margin:0 0 10px; font-size:18px; letter-spacing:-.2px; }
    .card p{ margin:0 0 10px; color:var(--muted); }
    .list{ margin:0; padding-left:18px; color:var(--muted); }
    .list li{ margin:6px 0; }

    .steps{
      display:grid; gap:10px; margin-top:12px;
    }
    .step{
      border:1px dashed var(--border);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 12px 12px;
      background: rgba(246,247,251,.6);
    }
    .step b{ display:block; margin-bottom:4px; color:var(--text); }

    .cta{
      margin-top:16px;
      display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:10px;
    }
    .btn{
      display:inline-flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
      padding: 12px 14px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      border:1px solid var(--border);
      background: #fff;
      font-weight:700;
      min-width: 210px;
    }
    .btn.primary{
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent2));
      color:#fff;
      border-color: transparent;
    }
    .btn.primary:hover{ text-decoration:none; filter: brightness(1.03); }
    .btn:hover{ text-decoration:none; }

    .footer{
      margin-top:18px; color:var(--muted); font-size:12px;
      display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:10px; justify-content:space-between;
      padding: 14px 2px;
    }
    .fine{
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.70);
      border:1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 12px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 12px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="topbar">
      <div class="brand"><span class="dot"></span> Eviction Defense AI</div>
      <div class="pill">Educational tool • Not legal advice</div>
    </div>

    <section class="hero">
      <h1>Facing eviction?</h1>
      <p class="sub">
        This tool explains common eviction notices, typical timelines, and practical next steps in plain language.
        It’s designed to help you organize your situation quickly and avoid missing deadlines.
      </p>

      <div class="cta">
        <a class="btn" href="./docs/notice-types.md">Understand notice types</a>
        <a class="btn" href="./docs/timelines.md">See timelines</a>
        <a class="btn primary" href="https://store.webmastereric.com">Optional document kits</a>
      </div>

      <div class="grid">
        <div class="card">
          <h2>What this tool does</h2>
          <ul class="list">
            <li>Explains notice types and what they usually mean</li>
            <li>Outlines the general eviction process and timing</li>
            <li>Helps you identify what step you’re on</li>
            <li>Points you toward organized next actions</li>
          </ul>

          <div class="steps">
            <div class="step">
              <b>Step 1 — Identify your situation</b>
              Start with the notice type and any dates on your paperwork.
            </div>
            <div class="step">
              <b>Step 2 — Understand the timeline</b>
              See what often happens next so you can plan ahead.
            </div>
            <div class="step">
              <b>Step 3 — Take action fast</b>
              If you need structured documents, use the optional kits.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h2>What this tool is not</h2>
          <p>
            This is not a law firm and does not provide legal advice or representation.
            Laws vary by jurisdiction and by case facts.
          </p>
          <div class="fine">
            If you can, seek licensed legal help or local legal aid. This tool exists to educate and organize—especially when time is short.
          </div>

          <h2 style="margin-top:14px;">Core guides</h2>
          <ul class="list">
            <li><a href="./docs/eviction-process-overview.md">Eviction process overview</a></li>
            <li><a href="./docs/notice-types.md">Notice types</a></li>
            <li><a href="./docs/timelines.md">Timelines</a></li>
            <li><a href="./docs/what-you-can-do-now.md">What you can do now</a></li>
            <li><a href="./docs/legal-scope.md">Legal scope & disclaimer</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <div>Built by Webmaster Eric • Transparent self-help systems</div>
        <div><a href="https://store.webmastereric.com">store.webmastereric.com</a></div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</body>
</html>